text.section:
Subsection (1) of this section shall not prohibit:
Advertising in newspapers, magazines, or periodicals having a general circulation;
Promotional advertising on radio or television limited to no more than the name of the licensee and the products the licensee is permitted to manufacture or sell;
Promotional advertising containing the names of establishments or products displayed on uniforms or equipment of sporting teams; or
Promotional advertising mailed or delivered to a consumer's residence.
